    <mxCell id="n_note" value="How to read this&#10;&#10;• ONE orchestrator: the durable SessionWorkflow. When a build is needed it SPAWNS a child PipelineWorkflow — not a second brain.&#10;&#10;• Voice WS is the ONLY direct browser → arbiter path (latency exception). Everything else: browser → tacticl-core → arbiter (gRPC).&#10;&#10;• Deepgram + ElevenLabs are I/O adapters on the orchestrator ONLY. The pipeline is SILENT — no audio inside it.&#10;&#10;• tacticl-core is a FULL product backend (any size). Only LLM / orchestration work routes to arbiter.&#10;&#10;• Voice token: tacticl-core signs, arbiter verifies (shared Vault key)." style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#fff2cc;strokeColor=#d6b656;dashed=1;align=left;verticalAlign=top;fontSize=11;spacing=8;" vertex="1" parent="1">
      <mxGeometry x="770" y="200" width="400" height="250" as="geometry"/>
    </mxCell>

